Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.60,1:54:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, a response speech from the graduates.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.36,1:54:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin's Middle School Third-years, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.03,1:54:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.13,1:54:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Student Council President Isono Rinon acting as representative.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.32,1:55:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell response:
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.71,1:55:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it has become the season when all things have gone quiet and the sakura bloom.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.48,1:55:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Already we have sent off thirteen graduates,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.02,1:55:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But now the day has come when we ourselves must graduate Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.03,1:55:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We took for granted all the things we got to do with Sakura Gakuin,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.54,1:55:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we will no longer have these things after tomorrow hasn't sunk in for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.84,1:55:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Still I find myself wondering if we twelve are about to dance together tomorrow and after.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.29,1:55:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The very first year after I transferred in as a 5th-grader, I was the youngest member.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.15,1:55:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm middle school third-year.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.41,1:55:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As a senior member, I've been showered with supports and expectations of so many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.03,1:55:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and that made me stand before you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.72,1:55:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The first show I ever appeared in, from that moment on,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.23,1:56:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,began my life as a student of Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.03,1:56:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was the youngest member, I just dedicated myself to the lesson of my beloved dances everyday.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.31,1:56:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,, gathering multitudes of experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.88,1:56:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tried to keep up with the senpais
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.80,1:56:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,who were walking in front of me
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.16,1:56:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And once it came the time that we no longer had our senpai in front of us,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.43,1:56:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in our final school year, our worries were numerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.76,1:56:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This year's seniors all transferred in in different years:
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.92,1:56:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Myself in 2011, Saki in 2012,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.09,1:56:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and Shi-chan in 2013,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.03,1:56:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so honestly, I can't say we had been getting along very well till we turned seniors.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.49,1:56:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But once it was us three leading Sakura Gakuin,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.66,1:56:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we proved ourselves able by coming together in solidarity, and we managed to get through it a step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.48,1:57:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the events of this 2015 year for Sakura Gakuin was a record of six transfer students entering.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.59,1:57:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, the start of 2015 was marked by confusion and worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.31,1:57:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As the first and foremost instruction, we told transfer-ins the mental attitude as a Sakura Gakuin member.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.36,1:57:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, It was hard to understand for young girls and we got frustrated a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.42,1:57:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we're very determined to send kouhais what we've learned from senpais,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.34,1:57:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to make kouhais carry the good tradition of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.44,1:57:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and we spoke with them on this topic time and again until they understood the message.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.76,1:57:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We were very glad to see them all catching on little by little.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.88,1:57:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this year's group was half transfer-ins,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.13,1:57:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this year provided us with a newfound number of rewarding experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.21,1:57:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Soyo
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.59,1:58:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you overcoming your self-doubt in your ability bit by bit,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.03,1:58:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it made me happy and encouraged me as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.05,1:58:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that you will be able to improve your skills even further.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.68,1:58:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.58,1:58:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem shy at times, but I think there is much about yourself which you are keeping hidden.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.73,1:58:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So next year, please show us a side of Kano which is yet unknown to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.77,1:58:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Marin
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.05,1:58:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first transferred in, it was as if you could not speak at all due to shyness.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.89,1:58:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I look at you now, the way you interact with everyone instead of acting alone,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.30,1:58:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you speak with all of us, makes it apparent that you have changed greatly since you transferred in.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.50,1:58:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lend your unique worldview to Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.76,1:58:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maaya
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.07,1:58:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You are tall, but you have the face of a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.89,1:59:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it to be one of your better qualities, seldom though you show it, but I am also very fond of your composed demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.10,1:59:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, when you have become a middle school student, I want to see you become more like an elder sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.21,1:59:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoko
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.52,1:59:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're actually a very hard-worker.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.29,1:59:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and have your own opinion in several things which you seldom tell us.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.38,1:59:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you have made an effort to understand everything we taught you since the first day you transferred in.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.57,1:59:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know how hard you've been trying, I would like for you to improve your excellent dancing further.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.04,1:59:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you can do it in a way that only you can, and I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.23,1:59:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirena
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.76,1:59:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As a middle school second-year transfer, I imagine you also faced your share of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.58,1:59:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you just transferred in this year, you will still be a senior next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.17,1:59:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried not to show your worries, but I have noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.14,1:59:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think only Mirena can understand the mind of the new transfer-ins fully.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.62,1:59:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you become a good senpai who is considerate to the feeling of transfer-ins
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.15,2:00:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In this year, we often saw you became a peacemaker among new transfer-ins. So I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.14,2:00:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Megu
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.44,2:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This year, the way you dealt with your kouhai made it seem like you have matured.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.44,2:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Time and again you astounded me with your grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.95,2:00:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can pass on your grace to kouhais as a Sakura girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.87,2:00:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you speak, because there will be times when you can see things objectively,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.06,2:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you refine your talking and can show your personality more next year.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.40,2:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.67,2:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year you will be the longest tenured member of Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.48,2:00:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you realise the mind of senpais well.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.48,2:00:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know better than any the goals of a senpai.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.96,2:00:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially for things like the meaning of song lyrics and choreography,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.65,2:00:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,please pass down the traditions of Sakura Gakuin to your kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.76,2:00:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.95,2:00:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year you will be a third-year in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.19,2:01:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You really shined while we were charging through the last leg of this 2015 year.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.54,2:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how much consideration you have put into Sakura Gakuin and how much concern you have for the group.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.27,2:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come to carry out what you've thought.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.64,2:01:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can convey your feelings to those around you, then everyone will prosper as you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.04,2:01:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and give a vigorous reprimand to bad. I hope you can be such kind of a senior.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.76,2:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the context of this year's changes, I have come to know the value of our graduates.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.20,2:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I often consulted the graduates because I did not want to present my weakness to kouhais.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.47,2:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I received a lot of advice from them.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.87,2:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is on account of all the graduates that we can be on this big stage.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.06,2:01:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for your watching over Sakura Gakuin all this time.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.75,2:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I think the greatest source of strength for Sakura Gakuin is the fukei-sans.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.44,2:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can clearly recall the faces I saw when I looked out from the stage at my first performance.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.83,2:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As the years went by, I could see more and more flags. I am so grateful to so many people who come to know Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.80,2:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to stand on this stage as part of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.22,2:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and being able to perform are things we should not take for granted.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.36,2:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To the fukei, the graduates, the staff,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.15,2:02:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and our teachers, we're grateful for your support, without which we would not find ourselves in this setting.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.30,2:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the many experiences we had as members of Sakura Gakuin, we could reinvent ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.28,2:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We will continue to smile our best to strive for our own paths to becoming super ladies.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.11,2:02:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we part, we will be united, and we will not ever forget the fukei-sans,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.83,2:03:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the time we spent in Sakura Gakuin will become a treasured memory.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.95,2:03:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly thank you for what you have done for me so far.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.72,2:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue to support both us and Sakura Gakuin henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.75,2:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-seventh March, the 28th year of the Heisei Era,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.12,2:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,2015 Sakura Gakuin graduates' representative, Isono Rinon.
